---
title: Bison and Wild Mushroom Pizza with Walnuts and Pesto
description: A fungi flatbread with a wild twist! Spiced ground bison and earthy mushrooms are a match made in heaven. Chopped walnuts and a pesto drizzle make this a restaurant-worthy flatbread!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pizza-au-bison-et-aux-champignons-sauvages-6a90ad43.jpg
